      "start": 798.32,
      "end": 801.6,
      "text": "네, 이제 커스터머가 계속 좀 더 구체적으로 질문을 하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 801.72,
      "end": 803.06,
      "text": "원래 이렇게까지 안 물어봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 803.08,
      "end": 804.3,
      "text": "How did she die?"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.42,
      "end": 805.56,
      "text": "How did she die?"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.64,
      "end": 806.74,
      "text": "어떻게 돌아가셨는데요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.3,
      "end": 807.86,
      "text": "Cancer."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.28,
      "end": 808.8,
      "text": "아무뤄요."
    },
    {
      "start": 809.24,
      "end": 811.36,
      "text": "Oh, I'm so sorry to hear that."
    },
    {
      "start": 811.62,
      "end": 812.5,
      "text": "Who was she?"
    },
    {
      "start": 812.66,
      "end": 814.3,
      "text": "오, 유감이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 814.62,
      "end": 814.98,
      "text": "그러면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 814.98,
      "end": 816.46,
      "text": "Who was she?"
    },
    {
      "start": 816.64,
      "end": 817.12,
      "text": "이렇게까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 817.12,
      "end": 818.22,
      "text": "She's being nosy."
    },
    {
      "start": 818.44,
      "end": 819.78,
      "text": "Very nosy."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.1,
      "end": 821.28,
      "text": "어지럽고 너무 부린 것 같이네."
    },
    {
      "start": 821.28,
      "end": 821.78,
      "text": "그녀요."
    },
    {
      "start": 822.3,
      "end": 822.9,
      "text": "누구였는데요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 823.14,
      "end": 824.42,
      "text": "라고까지 물어봤어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 824.42,
      "end": 826.64,
      "text": "네, do you know the owner까지는 괜찮은데."
    },
    {
      "start": 827.2,
      "end": 828.34,
      "text": "How did she die?"
    },
    {
      "start": 828.42,
      "end": 829.68,
      "text": "Who was she?"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.46,
      "end": 833.22,
      "text": "Oh, I'm so sorry to hear that."
    },
    {
      "start": 833.28,
      "end": 833.84,
      "text": "Who was she?"
    },
    {
      "start": 834.04,
      "end": 834.54,
      "text": "이미 했고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 834.8,
      "end": 835.96,
      "text": "Nice choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 836.44,
      "end": 837.72,
      "text": "잘 고르셨네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 838.36,
      "end": 839.58,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "start": 839.7,
      "end": 840.14,
      "text": "감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 840.14,
      "end": 842.38,
      "text": "Yes, she ignores her."
    },
    {
      "start": 842.48,
      "end": 842.98,
      "text": "네, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 843.2,
      "end": 845.92,
      "text": "여기서도 거두절미하고 대답만 탁 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 846.26,
      "end": 847.08,
      "text": "이제 그 다음에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 847.08,
      "end": 849.46,
      "text": "Marthaka came into her apartment."
    },
    {
      "start": 849.72,
      "end": 852.72,
      "text": "들어와서 혼자서 이제 내레이션이 이어지는 부분입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 853.36,
      "end": 856.32,
      "text": "I've lived in the same apartment for 46 years."
    },
    {
      "start": 856.56,
      "end": 860.24,
      "text": "나는 이 아파트에서 46년을 살았죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 860.24,
      "end": 862.32,
      "text": "So she is the owner of the apartment."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.32,
      "end": 862.98,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 863.12,
      "end": 864.64,
      "text": "And she's the one who has cancer."
    },
    {
      "start": 864.86,
      "end": 865.42,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 866.45,
      "end": 868.09,
      "text": "I don't know where the years have gone."
    },
    {
      "start": 868.59,
      "end": 870.17,
      "text": "여기에서 이 문장을 이야기합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.35,
      "end": 872.27,
      "text": "I don't know where the years have gone."
    },
    {
      "start": 872.77,
      "end": 875.25,
      "text": "어느새 세월이 이렇게 흘러버린 걸까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 875.25,
      "end": 876.61,
      "text": "Oh, my God."
    },
    {
      "start": 877.17,
      "end": 879.71,
      "text": "My mom, she used to say we don't die."
    },
    {
      "start": 880.09,
      "end": 883.47,
      "text": "We live on through the memories we leave behind."
    },
    {
      "start": 884.47,
      "end": 888.03,
      "text": "이 이야기를 할 때는 자신의 소지품 정리하다가"
    },
    {
      "start": 888.03,
      "end": 891.61,
      "text": "어렸을 때 찍혔던 사진들을 보면서 하는 말이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 892.43,
      "end": 895.17,
      "text": "맙소사, my mom, 우리 엄마는"
    },
    {
      "start": 895.17,
      "end": 897.79,
      "text": "She used to say, 말씀하곤 하셨죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 897.91,
      "end": 898.71,
      "text": "We don't die."
    },
    {
      "start": 898.87,
      "end": 900.05,
      "text": "우리가 죽지 않을 거라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.85,
      "end": 901.53,
      "text": "그런 다음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 901.53,
      "end": 904.85,
      "text": "We live on through the memories we leave behind."
    },
    {
      "start": 904.85,
      "end": 907.03,
      "text": "우리가 남긴 추억을 통해"
    },
    {
      "start": 907.03,
      "end": 909.95,
      "text": "그 추억들을 안고서 살아간다고 하셨죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 910.37,
      "end": 911.85,
      "text": "이렇게 이야기를 했습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 911.85,
      "end": 912.49,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 912.75,
      "end": 914.51,
      "text": "You leave memories to your loved ones."
    },
    {
      "start": 914.59,
      "end": 916.45,
      "text": "And you live on through those."
    },
    {
      "start": 916.65,
      "end": 917.07,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 917.35,
      "end": 917.47,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 918.13,
      "end": 920.45,
      "text": "이 첫 장면 한 번 더 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 921.13,
      "end": 922.97,
      "text": "I just love estate sales, you know,"
    },
    {
      "start": 923.03,
      "end": 926.33,
      "text": "because they like give you a glimpse into a person's life."
    },
    {
      "start": 926.85,
      "end": 927.45,
      "text": "8350."
    },
    {
      "start": 928.37,
      "end": 930.37,
      "text": "Did you know the owner?"
    },
    {
      "start": 932.18,
      "end": 932.76,
      "text": "I did."
    },
    {
      "start": 933.22,
      "end": 934.06,
      "text": "How did she die?"
    },
    {
      "start": 934.89,
      "end": 935.31,
      "text": "Cancer."
    },
    {
      "start": 935.31,
      "end": 937.57,
      "text": "Oh, I'm so sorry to hear that."
    },
    {
      "start": 937.97,
      "end": 938.53,
      "text": "Who was she?"
    },
    {
      "start": 939.23,
      "end": 939.83,
      "text": "Nice choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 940.47,
      "end": 941.51,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "start": 942.36,
      "end": 946.22,
      "text": "I have lived in this same apartment for 46 years."
    },
    {
      "start": 947.5,
      "end": 949.96,
      "text": "I don't know where the years have gone."
    },
    {
      "start": 950.5,
      "end": 951.36,
      "text": "Oh my god."
    },
    {
      "start": 952.55,
      "end": 953.55,
      "text": "Ah, my mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 954.09,
      "end": 955.63,
      "text": "She used to say that we don't die."
    },
    {
      "start": 956.39,
      "end": 958.81,
      "text": "We live on through the memories we leave behind."
    },
    {
      "start": 958.81,
      "end": 979.87,
      "text": "And this movie really is honestly adorable."
    },
    {
      "start": 979.87,
      "end": 982.21,
      "text": "Light, cute, easy to watch."
    },
    {
      "start": 982.21,
      "end": 985.51,
      "text": "자, 우리 크쌤은 내일 다시 만날게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 985.91,
      "end": 986.33,
      "text": "아우, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 986.51,
      "end": 987.01,
      "text": "내일 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 987.49,
      "end": 988.99,
      "text": "좀 빨리 가라앉는 듯이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 989.57,
      "end": 990.37,
      "text": "Bye-bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 990.45,
      "end": 990.67,
      "text": "Bye."
    }
  ]
}